WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.300 --> 00:00:04.466
You really can't seize the opportunity, can you?

2
00:00:04.533 --> 00:00:06.166
You could have lived.

3
00:00:06.266 --> 00:00:07.800
It's hard to say.

4
00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:09.466
Now Sophie is okay.

5
00:00:09.466 --> 00:00:10.500
Can't stop me

6
00:00:11.100 --> 00:00:12.366
Still so confident

7
00:00:12.366 --> 00:00:14.866
Even without Sophie, you're hurt

8
00:00:14.966 --> 00:00:16.300
Tell me again

9
00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:18.100
You don't know that?

10
00:00:18.100 --> 00:00:21.266
I, Ma Liang, you have the ability to speak

11
00:00:21.266 --> 00:00:23.333
I am on the pen now

12
00:00:23.333 --> 00:00:24.566
The condition is excellent

13
00:00:24.700 --> 00:00:26.600
Baby close your eyes

14
00:00:31.300 --> 00:00:33.833
The deception is really cunning

15
00:00:34.400 --> 00:00:37.466
Hmph, I thought you had something to do

16
00:00:37.866 --> 00:00:40.966
It seems that you are also a senior reporter

17
00:00:42.133 --> 00:00:44.833
Why was Ma Liang injured so badly?

18
00:00:45.066 --> 00:00:46.300
Who did it?

19
00:00:46.500 --> 00:00:47.800
Who else could it be?

20
00:00:47.800 --> 00:00:49.433
You gave me a knife

21
00:00:49.933 --> 00:00:50.800
Me.

22
00:00:51.900 --> 00:00:53.466
How could I hurt you?

23
00:00:53.466 --> 00:00:54.900
Do I have to lie?

24
00:00:54.900 --> 00:00:57.700
I'm sorry, it's the chick who should apologize

25
00:00:57.800 --> 00:00:59.500
Where are we now?

26
00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:01.466
Three-headed Ridge is here

27
00:01:01.466 --> 00:01:03.100
We found three hills

